snippet.textDisplay: This just isn't funny. SNL is little more than a minstrel show, and Eddie Murphy hasn't had an original joke since the early to mid 1990's. This whole skit is a rip-off from Dave Chappelle. Plagiarism is never funny. But 11million people on the internet are probably racists. Glorifying poor choices and bad behavior isn't comedy, and it's probably only funny if your a racist bigot or a self-flagellating black comedian. Chapelle at least had the 20lb brass testicles to include a white guy and an Asian with the contestants. The clueless asian and the urban culture white guy were the funny part. This? This is just fucking sad. Whoever let this unfunny trash on the air should be fired from NBC and... Oh, NBC's been on a racist streak since the 80's, and SNL hasn't been the place where comedians get their break since the 70's. Lately, SNL is just where washed up sellouts go to score an eight-ball. Thank God I don't have cable TV.
